-- FDIC says cannot comment on "speculative reports" about bad bank
-- 
-- Wed Jan 28, 2009 11:31am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/28/us-fdic-badbank-idUSTRE50R51820090128

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Federal Deposit Insurance Corp spokesman told Reuters on Wednesday it cannot comment on "speculative reports" regarding any FDIC role with potential government-run bad bank to soak up banks' toxic assets. 

